<plot>Danny is in Anger Therapy classes due to his public displays of violence and rage. His home life is a disaster in the form of the most controlling Mother ever. His daily life leads him to inescapable social annoyances and awkwardness. One day he meets a girl, a French girl named Marie, who is possibly the only person that can connect with him. She offers the chance of a different life. The only question for Danny now is can he control his rage long enough to not blow it?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?078915</url></doc>
